      "weather": "Overcast",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LENNY'S HONEY (2) hit the ground running and set it up early clocking 19.54 with a half a length win at Murray Bridge Straight over 350m. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. JALAPENO GEM (5) jumped from box 8 last time and ran away with an impressive win scoring by 5.5 lengths at this track in a handy 31.03. Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. In form and can go on with it. CANYA VIVI (1) could manage only third at Gawler last time but turned heads when posting a sharp 37.65 over 643m at Gawler the start prior. Should be in this for a long way. KEELEY ROSE (8) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
